onus and I got to compete in front of my family, my kids.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I got to be flag bearer.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So yeah, bucket list ticked off on every occasion.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": []}]}"